<h1
  style='margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #1C1B2E; letter-spacing: -0.01em;'
>
  Reset your password
</h1>

<p
  style='margin: 0 0 24px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6B6878; line-height: 1.6;'
>
  You requested a password reset. Click the button below to set a new one.
</p>

<a
  href='{{resetUrl}}'
  style='display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #E8572E; color: #FFFFFF; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500;'
>
  Reset my password
</a>

<p
  style='margin: 24px 0 0 0; font-size: 12px; color: #6B6878; line-height: 1.6;'
>
  This link expires in
  <strong style='color: #1C1B2E;'>1 hour</strong>.<br />
  If the button does not work, copy this link into your browser:<br />
  <span style='color: #E8572E; word-break: break-all;'>{{resetUrl}}</span>
</p>